# Phase 3 of Feature P: catalog working copy. Blob is the source of
# truth; `.catalog/` is populated by `npm run catalog:pull` and
# consumed by tests + the generator script. `.catalog/.snapshot/`
# tracks the last-pulled state so `npm run catalog:push` can detect
# remote drift before overwriting.
.catalog/
